    "go on a massive editing spree of... Maybe create some... Some beads that have enough references to enough contexts that... Yeah, this is kind of large, so you kind of need to think wide. Like start documenting what this all means, and probably just use reports … I guess you could use agents and just send them on components to do some architecture stuff and leave a note, maybe. That says must implement."
