    "Macro grammar gap. Signal channel stream block requires a request side retract variant for string close. So let's redesign the macro. Let's make it a way to create a closing variant for each scenario. Let's look at this together."
    "Authorizing macro redesign on the stream-close grammar. The fix lets each contract name its own close verb instead of inheriting the universal Retract shape."
